dc_title_s: Geologic map of New York exhibiting the structure of the state so far as known: South Western sheet
dc_description_s: Companion text: Description of the state geologic map of 1901 / Frederick J. H. Merrill. Albany : University of the State of New York / New York State Museum, 1902. Bulletin 56. 42p. 2 pls. Alternate title: Geologic map of New York: South Western sheet. Map is 22 sheets stored in box on top of New York map cases. Insets: New York City and Long Island Sound, boroughs of New York City. Section maps included. Geology shown by coloring.
dc_publisher_s: [Albany, NY] : University of the State of New York, New York State Museum, 1901.
